I"ã<ol>
  <li>Edit Docker Systemd Service (<code class="highlighter-rouge">EDITOR=vim systemctl edit docker</code>):
    <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>[Service]
ExecStart=
ExecStart=/usr/bin/dockerd -H tcp://0.0.0.0:2375 -H unix:///var/run/docker.sock
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Restart Docker Daemon:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>systemctl restart docker
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ol>

